    "en": {
        "FROSTHEX_ASTERIA_NAME": "Sorceress",
        "FROSTHEX_ASTERIA_DESCRIPTION": "The Sorceress is a mobile, short-range mage with a focus on Area-of-Effect abilities that excel at dealing with swarms of weak enemies.<color=#CCD3E0>\n\n< ! > Shadowflame is a stacking damage-over-time debuff that grants a small amount of life to anyone damaging an enemy afflicted by it.\n\n< ! > Use Rend to effectively deal with large groups of nearby enemies.\n\n< ! > Shadowshot can be used to push enemies to a safe distance or pull them into range.\n\n< ! > Nova Warp grants brief invincibility on use and damages nearby enemies. Use it to reposition to safety or put out some extra damage.\n\n< ! > Gravity Well deals large AOE damage, but leaves you immobile.\n\n\n\nTranslated by: Jaosnake. Original mod by Frosthex.",
        "FROSTHEX_ASTERIA_SUBTITLE": "The Void Mage",
        "FROSTHEX_ASTERIA_LORE": "...Lore? Do I look like the main character to you?",
        "FROSTHEX_ASTERIA_OUTRO_FLAVOR": "..and so she left, in search of new worlds to explore.",
        "FROSTHEX_ASTERIA_OUTRO_FAILURE": "..and so she vanished, forever doomed to obscurity.",
        "FROSTHEX_ASTERIA_MASTERY_SKIN_NAME": "<color=#9933CC>Crimson</color>",
        "FROSTHEX_ASTERIA_LUNAR_SKIN_NAME": "<color=#9933CC>Blue Flame</color>",
        "FROSTHEX_ASTERIA_PASSIVE_NAME": "<color=#9933CC>Astral Flight</color>",
        "FROSTHEX_ASTERIA_PASSIVE_DESCRIPTION": "The Sorceress can glide while falling for 5 seconds. Some attacks have a chance to apply <color=#9933CC>Shadowflame</color>.\n\nTranslated by: Jaosnake. Original mod by Frosthex.",
        "FROSTHEX_ASTERIA_NO_JUMP_NAME": "<color=#9933CC>Astral Flight: Tradewinds</color>",
        "FROSTHEX_ASTERIA_NO_JUMP_DESCRIPTION": "The Sorceress can glide while falling for 5 seconds. Some attacks have a chance to apply <color=#9933CC>Shadowflame</color>. Hopoo Feathers are converted into 0.5s of max flight time each.\n\nTranslated by: Jaosnake. Original mod by Frosthex.",
        "FROSTHEX_ASTERIA_NORMAL_JUMP_NAME": "<color=#9933CC>Astral Flight: Updraft</color>",
        "FROSTHEX_ASTERIA_NORMAL_JUMP_DESCRIPTION": "The Sorceress can glide while falling for 5 seconds. Some attacks have a chance to apply <color=#9933CC>Shadowflame</color>. Hopoo Feathers each grant one jump.\n\nTranslated by: Jaosnake. Original mod by Frosthex.",
        "FROSTHEX_ASTERIA_PRIMARY_SLASH_NAME": "<color=#9933CC>Rend</color>",
        "FROSTHEX_ASTERIA_PRIMARY_SLASH_DESCRIPTION": "<style=cIsUtility>Agile</style>. <color=#9933CC>Aerial</color>. Swing for <style=cIsDamage>200% damage</style>, with a 50% chance to apply <color=#9933CC>Shadowflame</color>. Every third attack applies Shadowflame, <style=cIsUtility>restores a small amount of flight time</style>, and deals <color=#9933CC>double damage</color>.\n\nTranslated by: Jaosnake. Original mod by Frosthex.",
        "FROSTHEX_ASTERIA_PRIMARY_WHIP_NAME": "<color=#9933CC>Pierce</color>",
        "FROSTHEX_ASTERIA_PRIMARY_WHIP_DESCRIPTION": "<style=cIsUtility>Agile</style>. <color=#9933CC>Aerial</color>. Fire a short-range, infinitely piercing beam for <style=cIsDamage>200% damage</style> with a 50% chance to apply <color=#9933CC>Shadowflame</color>.\n\nTranslated by: Jaosnake. Original mod by Frosthex.",
        "FROSTHEX_ASTERIA_SECONDARY_GUN_NAME": "<color=#9933CC>Shadowshot</color>",
        "FROSTHEX_ASTERIA_SECONDARY_GUN_DESCRIPTION": "Shoot a spectral arrow, dealing <style=cIsDamage>540% damage</style>. On-hit, creates a black hole that pulls in nearby enemies. If used while gliding, redirects your momentum towards the shot.\n\nTranslated by: Jaosnake. Original mod by Frosthex.",
        "FROSTHEX_ASTERIA_SPECIAL_PILLAR_NAME": "<color=#9933CC>Rupture</color>",
        "FROSTHEX_ASTERIA_SPECIAL_PILLAR_DESCRIPTION": "<style=cIsUtility>Agile</style>. <color=#9933CC>Aerial</color>. Conjure a beam of energy, dealing <style=cIsDamage>700% damage</style> to all enemies inside over 0.5 seconds. Aiming at nearby terrain summons a larger pillar that does <style=cIsDamage>twice as much damage.</style>\n\nTranslated by: Jaosnake. Original mod by Frosthex.",
        "FROSTHEX_ASTERIA_UTILITY_WARP_NAME": "<color=#9933CC>Nova Warp</color>",
        "FROSTHEX_ASTERIA_UTILITY_WARP_DESCRIPTION": "<color=#9933CC>Aerial</color>. <style=cIsUtility>Warp a short distance</style>, detonating on ending for <style=cIsDamage>600% damage</style>. Holds 2 charges.\n\nTranslated by: Jaosnake. Original mod by Frosthex.",
        "FROSTHEX_ASTERIA_UTILITY_LAUNCH_NAME": "<color=#9933CC>Second Wind</color>",
        "FROSTHEX_ASTERIA_UTILITY_LAUNCH_DESCRIPTION": "<color=#9933CC>Aerial</color>. <style=cIsUtility>Launch yourself into the air</style>, fully restoring flight time.\n\nTranslated by: Jaosnake. Original mod by Frosthex.",
        "FROSTHEX_ASTERIA_SPECIAL_WELL_NAME": "<color=#9933CC>Gravity Well</color>",
        "FROSTHEX_ASTERIA_SPECIAL_WELL_DESCRIPTION": "Create a pocket dimension around yourself, repeatedly dealing <style=cIsDamage>160% damage</style> to all enemies inside, scaling with attack speed. Has a small chance to apply <color=#9933CC>Shadowflame</color> on-hit.\n\nTranslated by: Jaosnake. Original mod by Frosthex.",
        "FROSTHEX_ASTERIA_SPECIAL_RAM_NAME": "<color=#9933CC>Living Comet</color>",
        "FROSTHEX_ASTERIA_SPECIAL_RAM_DESCRIPTION": "<color=#9933CC>Aerial</color>. <style=cIsUtility>Heavy</style>. Surge forward for 1.5 seconds, gaining 10% barrier and dealing <style=cIsDamage>200 - 2500% damage</style> to enemies you run into, scaling with movement speed. <color=#9933CC>Applies Shadowflame</color>. Holds 2 charges.\n\nTranslated by: Jaosnake. Original mod by Frosthex.",
        "FROSTHEX_ASTERIA_SCEPTER_WELL_NAME": "<color=#9933CC>Subsume</color>",
        "FROSTHEX_ASTERIA_SCEPTER_WELL_DESCRIPTION": "Create a pocket dimension around yourself, pulling nearby enemies towards the center and repeatedly dealing <style=cIsDamage>160% damage</style> to all enemies inside, scaling with attack speed. Has a small chance to apply <color=#9933CC>Shadowflame</color> on-hit. At the end, implode for <style=cIsDamage>400% damage</style>.\n\nTranslated by: Jaosnake. Original mod by Frosthex.",
        "FROSTHEX_ASTERIA_SCEPTER_RAM_NAME": "<color=#9933CC>Arcane Comet</color>",
        "FROSTHEX_ASTERIA_SCEPTER_RAM_DESCRIPTION": "<color=#9933CC>Aerial</color>. <style=cIsUtility>Heavy</style>. Restores half of flight time. Surge forward for 1.5 seconds, extended by 0.5 for each bash, gaining 20% barrier and dealing <style=cIsDamage>200 - 2500% damage</style> to enemies you run into, scaling with movement speed. <color=#9933CC>Applies Shadowflame</color>. Holds 3 charges.\n\nTranslated by: Jaosnake. Original mod by Frosthex.",
        "ACHIEVEMENT_FROSTHEX_ASTERIA_MASTERYACHIEVEMENT_NAME": "Sorceress: Mastery",
        "ACHIEVEMENT_FROSTHEX_ASTERIA_MASTERYACHIEVEMENT_DESCRIPTION": "As Sorceress, beat the game or obliterate on Monsoon.\n\nTranslated by: Jaosnake. Original mod by Frosthex.",
        "ACHIEVEMENT_FROSTHEX_ASTERIA_ECLIPSEACHIEVEMENT_NAME": "Sorceress: Eclipsed",
        "ACHIEVEMENT_FROSTHEX_ASTERIA_ECLIPSEACHIEVEMENT_DESCRIPTION": "As Sorceress, beat the game on Eclipse 8.\n\nTranslated by: Jaosnake. Original mod by Frosthex.",
        "ACHIEVEMENT_FROSTHEX_ASTERIA_SPEEDACHIEVEMENT_NAME": "Sorceress: Speed. Violence. Momentum.",
        "ACHIEVEMENT_FROSTHEX_ASTERIA_SPEEDACHIEVEMENT_DESCRIPTION": "As Sorceress, maintain a flight speed of 70 m/s or higher for 2 seconds.\n\nTranslated by: Jaosnake. Original mod by Frosthex.",
        "ACHIEVEMENT_FROSTHEX_ASTERIA_AIRTIMEACHIEVEMENT_NAME": "Sorceress: Can't Touch This",
        "ACHIEVEMENT_FROSTHEX_ASTERIA_AIRTIMEACHIEVEMENT_DESCRIPTION": "As Sorceress, stay airborne for 30 seconds without landing.\n\nTranslated by: Jaosnake. Original mod by Frosthex."
    },
